    "The conversations in the initial training phase were considered as comparison data.",
    "For this, one randomly selected model-generated message was sampled to some alternative responses and all these samples were ranked by AI trainers.",
    "After that, the model was fine-tuned through these reward models.Interaction with ChatGPT can be divided into Query and Response.",
    "Generally, a user can make a Query to the ChatGPT.",
    "This query is directly processed by the GPT-4."
